summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5398 for the improvement of the north 410 feet of the Alley in Block 6, H.S. Turner Park Addition, being the north 410 feet of the alley between 25th Avenue North and 26th Avenue North, from East Newton Street to the north line of Interlaken Addition; by paving and otherwise improving the same.
